        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nCurrently the Jenkins jobs will only retrieve the version.properties file located at the root of the repo, which means that all artifacts from the same repo will have the same version.  To support having different artifacts in the same repo, we probably need LF to add such a feature to the Jenkins job templates.",
